Stephen R. Hardis







Stephen R. Hardis
Experience
Steve retired as the chairman and chief executive officer of Eaton Corporation (NYSE: ETN), where he served in executive roles during his more than 20 years at the firm. He is the former chairman of the board of Marsh & McLennan Companies, Inc. (NYSE: MMC) and is lead director of Axcelis Technologies, Inc. (NASDAQ: ACLS) and Progressive Corporation (NYSE: PGR). He is also a director of Lexmark International Corporation (NYSE: LXK) and Parkwood Corporation. and is an emeritus trustee of The Cleveland Clinic.













